You need to order the results for pagination to work reliably.
For example, the integration tests fail on my local environment because the ordering is different.
Can be fixed using ORDER BY

    sqlStringBuilder.append(" ORDER BY anchor_id");
or even:

    sqlStringBuilder.append(" ORDER BY anchor.name");

You can remove dataspace field since you know the anchors belong to the same dataspace. This can be then simplified to:

    @Query(value = "SELECT * FROM fragment WHERE anchor_id IN (:anchorIds) AND xpath IN (:xpaths)", 
            nativeQuery = true)
    List<FragmentEntity> findByAnchorIdsAndXpathIn(@Param("anchorIds") Long[] anchorIds, 
                                                   @Param("xpaths") String[] xpaths);

